Write the XHTML tag and event handler to pop up an alert message that says "Welcome" when the user clicks a button.

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>welcome</title>
</head>
<body>
    <button type="button" onclick="alert(welcome)">click me</button>
</body>
</html>
